trans-unit.source: Enables the <xref href="System.Web.DynamicData.DynamicDataManager"></xref> to declaratively define data controls that it manages.
trans-unit.target: Aktiverar den <xref href="System.Web.DynamicData.DynamicDataManager"> </xref> deklarativt definiera datakontroller som den hanterar.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.DynamicData.DataControlReference"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Web.DynamicData.DataControlReference"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: Gets the ID of the data-bound control that is managed by the <xref href="System.Web.DynamicData.DynamicDataManager"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar ID för den databundna kontrollen som hanteras av den <xref href="System.Web.DynamicData.DynamicDataManager"> </xref> kontroll.

trans-unit.source: The ID of the data-bound control that is managed by the <xref href="System.Web.DynamicData.DynamicDataManager"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: ID för den databundna kontrollen som hanteras av den <xref href="System.Web.DynamicData.DynamicDataManager"> </xref> kontroll.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref href="System.Web.DynamicData.DynamicDataManager"></xref> control that contains the data control.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar den <xref href="System.Web.DynamicData.DynamicDataManager"> </xref> kontroll som innehåller data-kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.DynamicData.DynamicDataManager"></xref> control that contains the data control.
Gets the literal string `DataControl``:` that has the value of the <xref:System.Web.DynamicData.DataControlReference.ControlID%2A?displayProperty=fullName> control appended to it.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar den exakta strängen `DataControl``:` som har värdet för den <xref:System.Web.DynamicData.DataControlReference.ControlID%2A?displayProperty=fullName> kontroll läggs till den.

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Web.DynamicData.DataControlReference.ControlID%2A> property is empty or `null`, the literal string `DataControl` is returned.
trans-unit.target: Om den <xref:System.Web.DynamicData.DataControlReference.ControlID%2A>egenskapen är tom eller `null`, den exakta strängen `DataControl` returneras.</xref:System.Web.DynamicData.DataControlReference.ControlID%2A>

trans-unit.source: The literal string `DataControl:` that has the value of the <xref:System.Web.DynamicData.DataControlReference.ControlID%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property appended to it.
trans-unit.target: Den exakta strängen `DataControl:` som har värdet för den <xref:System.Web.DynamicData.DataControlReference.ControlID%2A?displayProperty=fullName> egenskap som läggs till den.
